Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.34,0:02:42.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.55,0:02:49.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you! Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.60,0:02:52.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone on the platform, please stand back!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.68,0:02:55.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We’ll need to see your tickets before boarding!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.19,0:02:58.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don’t push! No pushing, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.90,0:03:04.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, is this where car number four will be boarding?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.28,0:03:09.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, no, it’s not.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.74,0:03:11.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the first car.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.62,0:03:13.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Only VIPs can get in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.66,0:03:14.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.42,0:03:15.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aw, all that way?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.66,0:03:16.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What’s with him?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.83,0:03:20.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh my, that huge pack must be heavy!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.59,0:03:24.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He looks kind of handsome, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.05,0:03:26.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He must be one of those sandwich board advertisers.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.26,0:03:29.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, looks like it. Thank you so much, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.84,0:03:31.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me! Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.85,0:03:33.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.35,0:03:35.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.89,0:03:37.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.27,0:03:42.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stand back! Stand back!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.04,0:03:56.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me, everyone. Let me through.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.54,0:03:57.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.83,0:04:02.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for providing security, Detective.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.02,0:04:12.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aw man. It’s not fair!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.51,0:04:16.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to ride up there, with the mayor!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.23,0:04:17.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.48,0:04:20.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Will the train be back by this afternoon?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.44,0:04:26.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It loops back after four stops, so it should be less than an hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.37,0:04:34.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, this is a banner day!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.49,0:04:36.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Four more minutes!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.62,0:04:42.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I’d like to embark on the second stage as soon as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.71,0:04:45.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course! I trust you implicitly, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.88,0:04:47.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have our full support.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.34,0:04:50.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I’m Moria, from the Morning News.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.51,0:04:52.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Allow me to congratulate you on the new station.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.30,0:04:55.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How do you feel right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.14,0:05:00.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I’m extremely pleased to meet the expectations of my citizens.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.18,0:05:02.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I suppose that’s most of what I’m feeling.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.27,0:05:04.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well said, sir! Well said, indeed!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.94,0:05:04.78,Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,What suck-ups.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.78,0:05:05.57,Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\move(640,618,640,690,200,0)\t(50,200,\c&HE9ECF1&\3c&H262B32&)}What suck-ups.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.95,0:05:10.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, ink-slinger, let’s leave it at that, shall we?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.17,0:05:24.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Banzai!{\alpha&HFF&} Banzai! Banzai! Banzai! Banzai!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.96,0:05:26.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Banzai! Banzai!{\alpha&HFF&} Banzai! Banzai! Banzai!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.46,0:05:27.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Banzai! Banzai! Banzai!{\alpha&HFF&} Banzai! Banzai!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.67,0:05:28.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Banzai! Banzai! Banzai! Banzai!{\alpha&HFF&} Banzai!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.50,0:05:30.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Banzai! Banzai! Banzai! Banzai! Banzai!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.57,0:05:54.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This train’s atmosphere is so pleasant, isn’t it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.11,0:05:55.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, it is indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.28,0:05:59.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The riff-raff on my last ride were so unpleasant.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.12,0:06:01.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, well they are all rather rank.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.04,0:06:03.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I could barely breathe!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.59,0:06:16.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And the very first train, to boot!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.02,0:06:24.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I could hardly believe I won the drawing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.98,0:06:29.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I’ve so been looking forward to this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.06,0:06:31.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, so have I!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.39,0:07:47.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Was there an accident?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.90,0:07:49.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right. Everyone remain calm.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.69,0:07:51.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.44,0:07:53.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.87,0:07:59.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.24,0:08:01.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? What? Wha—
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.05,0:08:21.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Was it my imagination?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.77,0:08:23.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Mayor?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.68,0:08:24.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where’s everyone else?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.22,0:08:27.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where’d they go?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.22,0:08:27.02,Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,How did…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.02,0:08:29.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They’re all gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.15,0:08:31.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, thank you so much for earlier!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.90,0:08:33.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.19,0:08:38.49,Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}We apologize for the inconvenience.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.49,0:08:47.08,Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}We have discovered a foreign object blocking the tracks,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.07,0:08:44.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.70,0:08:47.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The first car.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.33,0:08:49.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The first car?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.08,0:08:51.09,Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}and are taking the necessary precautions.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.16,0:08:50.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.50,0:08:53.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.29,0:08:56.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, it’s nothing to shout about.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.21,0:08:59.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don’t be rude to the passengers.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.67,0:09:00.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But—
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.05,0:09:05.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Surely none of them have any\Ninsight into these strange occurrences.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.56,0:09:08.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.02,0:09:10.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,return to my seat, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.19,0:09:17.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll be going, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.79,0:09:30.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s too heavy!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.29,0:09:32.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can’t budge it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.41,0:09:35.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh. Let me try it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.13,0:09:37.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Useless women.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.17,0:09:39.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Kinoshita, the driver.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.30,0:09:42.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Station One, come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.76,0:09:48.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That’s strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.52,0:09:50.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Allow me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.93,0:09:52.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.02,0:09:55.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Old man just can’t contain himself, can he?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.57,0:10:00.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What’s the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.53,0:10:02.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why aren’t we moving?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.65,0:10:03.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.41,0:10:05.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What’s going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.32,0:10:06.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.95,0:10:13.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll have to have it modified so that anyone can open it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.34,0:10:20.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are the other cars?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.11,0:10:46.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Mayor?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.54,0:10:50.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who’s driving this thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.11,0:11:27.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll never forgive you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.30,0:11:44.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you just say you wouldn’t forgive me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.56,0:11:49.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you just say you wouldn’t forgive me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.69,0:11:55.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did anyone say that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.11,0:12:00.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.03,0:12:03.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was just my imagination.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.70,0:12:05.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no, how scary!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.49,0:12:07.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My imagination…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.79,0:12:07.08,Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,What’s the matter with this train?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.08,0:12:08.95,Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\move(640,616,640,690,200,0)\t(50,200,\c&HE9ECF1&\3c&H262B32&)}What’s the matter with this train?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.33,0:12:11.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren’t you in control?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.41,0:12:14.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I’ve used every tool at my disposal!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.37,0:12:16.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can’t even contact the surface.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.67,0:12:20.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll never get promoted now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.55,0:12:25.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought that today would go so well.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.09,0:12:25.59,Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,We’re in the tunnel the whole way, so it really is pretty scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.59,0:12:26.47,Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\move(640,616,640,690,200,0)\t(50,200,\c&HE9ECF1&\3c&H262B32&)}We’re in the tunnel the whole way, so it really is pretty scary.{mov}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.47,0:12:28.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We’re in the tunnel the whole way, so it really is pretty scary.{mov}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.51,0:12:28.89,Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,10:05 a.m., sudden stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.89,0:12:30.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Passengers vanish. Cause unknown.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.14,0:12:38.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey Newsman, don’t you get sick if you write on the train?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.78,0:12:44.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I’ve been doing my job for twenty years. I’m quite used to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.74,0:12:50.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What’s wrong, boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.24,0:12:52.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Goodness! Don’t scare me like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.91,0:12:52.83,Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,Um…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.46,0:12:56.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There was just a…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.81,0:13:13.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.93,0:13:15.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.23,0:13:17.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s the Sandwich Board Man.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.06,0:13:18.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Newsman!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.91,0:13:36.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.46,0:13:38.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There’re no other cars back there.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.50,0:13:41.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How’d you get in here?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.59,0:13:44.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As you saw,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.26,0:13:47.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I came from the next car along.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.05,0:13:52.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am a medicine seller.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.81,0:13:54.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.35,0:14:00.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to dress like this these days, for my wares to sell.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.48,0:14:03.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Still, it’s awfully pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.53,0:14:05.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You saw that, didn’t you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.32,0:14:09.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don’t know why, but we can’t get out of the door from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.70,0:14:15.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just a minute ago, the mayor…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.62,0:14:16.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fell out.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.96,0:14:21.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don’t finish his sentences! That’s creepy!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.46,0:14:25.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The train’s moving of its own accord.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.26,0:14:29.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s as though a fox spirit has a hold of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.68,0:14:34.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is not a fox spirit’s doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.51,0:14:35.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.97,0:14:36.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s just a figure of speech.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.85,0:14:39.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The mayor
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.85,0:14:42.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,was killed by a Mononoke.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.24,0:14:49.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A Mononoke?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.99,0:14:51.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop that! Don’t be creepy!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.82,0:14:53.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get your craziness out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.41,0:14:54.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was an accident, that’s all!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.33,0:14:56.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But the train’s moving on its own.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.24,0:14:56.41,Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course it was an accident!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.41,0:14:57.12,Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\move(640,618,640,690,200,0)\t(50,200,\c&HE9ECF1&\3c&H262B32&)}Of course it was an accident!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.12,0:14:58.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He’s yelling again.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.66,0:15:00.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You didn’t see anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.04,0:15:03.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can tell
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.84,0:15:05.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,even without having seen.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.30,0:15:07.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It moved by itself!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.40,0:15:25.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are those?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.15,0:15:28.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They’re{\alpha&HFF&} scales.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.11,0:15:29.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They’re scales.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.61,0:15:32.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Their alignment
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.24,0:15:36.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,tells me{\alpha&HFF&} the Mononoke’s position.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.54,0:15:39.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,tells me the Mononoke’s{\alpha&HFF&} position.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.54,0:15:41.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,tells me the Mononoke’s position.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.56,0:16:02.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are all connected.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.44,0:16:06.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Mononoke has placed all those involved in this car.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.90,0:16:09.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Connected? We’re all meeting for the first time.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.73,0:16:10.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That’s right!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.74,0:16:13.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just won my ticket in a raffle!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.53,0:16:13.66,Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,How would you say we’re connected?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.66,0:16:17.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should all know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.95,0:16:21.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think I do know one of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.00,0:16:21.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.96,0:16:24.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me too. I remember one person.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.92,0:16:27.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I remember one of you, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.50,0:16:28.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.50,0:16:29.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.30,0:16:34.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You too?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.09,0:16:36.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don’t know anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.05,0:16:39.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I’ve no idea what this is about, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.26,0:16:40.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.64,0:16:44.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To think that four of the six here recognize the same person.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.35,0:16:47.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you all be able to tell me more?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.61,0:16:50.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don’t remember any of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.57,0:16:51.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.86,0:16:55.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let’s have all your names, ages and\Nprofessions, along with where you say you met me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.95,0:16:58.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, right. That’s a good idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.24,0:17:00.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I’m Nomoto Chiyo, aged twenty-one.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.33,0:17:03.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I’m a waitress at a café across from the station!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.12,0:17:05.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A shining example of a career woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.29,0:17:08.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.46,0:17:10.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don’t be ridiculous!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.13,0:17:11.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I never went to that café!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.51,0:17:12.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes you did!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.80,0:17:15.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You came in on an investigation, didn’t you, Detective?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.84,0:17:17.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When was this?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.68,0:17:19.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Three or four months ago, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.01,0:17:20.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, exactly!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.06,0:17:21.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, how did…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.60,0:17:24.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Detective!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.98,0:17:30.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were outside smoking while your\Npartner questioned me, so I didn’t recognize you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.44,0:17:33.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah. I’m Yamaguchi Haru, a widow.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.28,0:17:34.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Age?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.15,0:17:34.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don’t be rude.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.82,0:17:37.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thirty-five.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.70,0:17:37.20,Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,You didn’t have to tell him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.20,0:17:40.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And what happened to your husband?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.28,0:17:43.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He died five years ago of an illness of the lungs.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.75,0:17:45.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I currently live with my mother-in-law.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.46,0:17:46.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just the facts, ma’am!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.96,0:17:48.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You really don’t remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.46,0:17:50.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unlike you, I’m a busy man!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.50,0:17:53.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can’t remember everyone I meet. Now, say when you met me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.13,0:17:56.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let’s see, what cures amnesia?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.13,0:17:56.47,Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,You have to give your name and age first, Detective.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.01,0:17:58.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You’re a willful young woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.14,0:18:01.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kadowaki Shakei, forty years old.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.81,0:18:03.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I’m a police officer.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.35,0:18:05.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I’ll give you a hint.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.10,0:18:07.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was about a regular customer at our shop.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.94,0:18:10.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One of those… Modern Girls, they call them.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.86,0:18:14.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That’s not all. She was totally gorgeous, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.78,0:18:17.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was so jealous!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.49,0:18:21.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unfortunately, though, she got hit by a train and died.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.24,0:18:22.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn’t mean to!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.54,0:18:31.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn’t mean to.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.04,0:18:32.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Morning News.{\alpha&HFF&} Train accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.88,0:18:34.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Morning News. Train accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.09,0:18:35.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.63,0:18:39.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That’s right. I remember. You\Nwere driving at the time, weren’t you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.05,0:18:40.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your name was…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.30,0:18:43.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kinoshita Bunpei, twenty-eight.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.60,0:18:45.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was just an accident!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.43,0:18:49.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She jumped off the bridge, killing herself, and\Nmy train just happened to be passing through.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.06,0:18:51.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jumped off…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.06,0:18:51.56,Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you then, I didn’t mean to do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.56,0:18:53.15,Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\move(640,618,640,690,200,0)\t(50,200,\c&HE9ECF1&\3c&H262B32&)}I told you then, I didn’t mean to do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.15,0:18:56.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We get it! Calm down. It wasn’t your fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.11,0:18:59.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We determined it was a clear suicide.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.11,0:18:57.78,Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.78,0:18:59.70,Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,So, that’s it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.70,0:19:02.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You look a bit pale.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.07,0:19:04.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shall I make you a tonic?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.83,0:19:07.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I’m fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.00,0:19:08.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.20,0:19:10.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Moria Kioshi.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.08,0:19:15.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Normally I have a desk job at a newspaper, but they\Nwere shorthanded today and sent me out in the field.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.67,0:19:18.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was the victim’s boss.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.59,0:19:21.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She was a writer, then? How nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.97,0:19:23.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She was pretty famous, if I remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.72,0:19:24.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What was her name?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.60,0:19:26.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I remember her now!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.68,0:19:28.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ichikawa Setsuko!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.14,0:19:31.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was so jealous that she had her name in the paper!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.44,0:19:33.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is some mistake!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.02,0:19:36.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don’t know any of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.90,0:19:40.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do I have to stay locked in here?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.03,0:19:42.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me off, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.82,0:19:44.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What does he mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.53,0:19:45.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.87,0:19:48.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what’s your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.08,0:19:49.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kobayashi Masao.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.62,0:19:50.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where do you go to school?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.79,0:19:54.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just graduated from elementary\Nschool, and I work delivering milk.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.67,0:19:56.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It must be hard, so early in the morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.21,0:19:58.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Morning?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.63,0:20:03.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I remember correctly, it was about 5\Na.m. when my train passed under the bridge.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.68,0:20:05.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kirigahara Bridge, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.06,0:20:09.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A delivery boy, you say.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.31,0:20:11.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That’s right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.89,0:20:14.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The dots are finally connected.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.51,0:20:42.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.43,0:20:45.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My word.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.05,0:20:48.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There was{\alpha&HFF&} a woman holding a cat, there.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.14,0:20:51.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There was a woman holding a cat, there.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.15,0:21:05.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s a Ghost Cat.
